snippet.title: LIVE: Alex Eala vs. Jessica Pegula | 2025 Miami Open Semifinals
snippet.description:
Fresh from her victory against four-time French Open champion Iga Swiatek, Filipina tennis ace Alex Eala now faces World No. 4 Jessica Pegula for a spot in the final round of the Miami Open on Friday (Manila time).
 
The match is being aired on A2Z Channel, Kapamilya Channel, and ABS-CBN News Channel.
 
The match is also streaming on the YouTube channels of ABS-CBN News, ANC 24/7 and ABS-CBN Sports plus Kapamilya Online Live for Philippine viewers only.
 
Eala, 19, has risen to No. 75 in the live WTA rankings after defeating Swiatek, World No. 25 Jelena Ostapenko and World No. 2 Madison Keys.
 
Pegula, a former World No. 3 player who reached as high as No. 1 in doubles, presents a formidable challenge to the Pinay.
 
Pegula previously advanced to the singles finals of the 2024 US Open and the 2023 WTA Finals and has won seven WTA singles titles.
 
She proceeded to the Miami Open semifinals after taking out Emma Raducanu of Great Britain, 6-4, 6-7(3), 6-2, in the quarterfinals on Thursday.
